You spot a pack of ferl ferrets roaming the woods.

ferl is the start of a trading platform. 

This content is released under the MIT License. So, have at it.

The name is pronounced fe*ral [feer-uhl, fer-] as in feral.  

0.1 Features:
- Trade Journal
- Back testing
- Simple indicators
- Paper trading
- A couple data feeds
- Start looking at FIX support
